        <li><a href="https://www.canva.com/" target="_blank" class="has-text-primary">Canva</a> - Create stunning visuals for social media and marketing.</li>
        <li><a href="https://www.shopify.com/" target="_blank" class="has-text-primary">Shopify (Free Trial)</a> - Build your online store easily.</li>
        <li><a href="https://analytics.google.com/" target="_blank" class="has-text-primary">Google Analytics</a> - Track and analyze your website traffic.</li>
        <li><a href="https://www.mailchimp.com/" target="_blank" class="has-text-primary">Mailchimp</a> - Manage email campaigns and grow your audience.</li>
        <li><a href="https://www.hootsuite.com/" target="_blank" class="has-text-primary">Hootsuite</a> - Schedule and manage social media posts in one place.</li>
        <li><a href="https://www.quickbooks.com/" target="_blank" class="has-text-primary">QuickBooks</a> - Manage your finances and track expenses efficiently.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

